1
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:09,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（以下劇情來自真實故事的啟發）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

2
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:12,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（某些角色與事件為創作與虛構）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

3
00:00:12,080 --> 00:00:13,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那感覺就像…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

4
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:17,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的太陽穴一陣陣刺痛</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但我的後腦杓也是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

5
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:20,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好像有火蟻在啃咬一樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在連我的視線也開始模糊了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

7
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我媽有多發性硬化症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

8
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這種痛感更像是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

9
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:34,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>結構性，而不是神經性的…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

10
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:38,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好像頭裡面長東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

11
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:43,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的醫生說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

12
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:45,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“我們不知道怎麼把你歸類</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

13
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:47,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不斷打破我們的預期”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

14
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:54,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我本來被宣判剩下六星期可活</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

15
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最多四個月</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

16
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是四年前的事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

17
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人類的潛力無窮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

18
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

19
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（貝兒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

20
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她是人母</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

21
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:14,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是癌症倖存者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

22
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是創業家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

23
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:21,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在還成了一位作家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

24
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，你是怎麼做到的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

25
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不知道，我想一旦你選擇抱持希望</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

26
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>萬事皆有可能</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

27
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:33,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>《神效蘋果醋》</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

28
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:38,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這位年輕辣媽剛剛從她的餐桌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

29
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>征服了矽谷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

30
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:42,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森的《健康廚坊》</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>與蘋果公司簽下大合約</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

31
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>多斐然的成就！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

32
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，你的健康如何？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

33
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>今天狀況很不錯，可以這麼說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

34
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:58,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她不顧醫囑，用自然方式自癒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

35
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>吸引了數百萬的粉絲追隨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

36
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

37
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是一個非比尋常的故事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

38
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:07,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是愛，帶給我力量與支持</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

39
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:10,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要感謝我的閨密和粉絲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

40
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:13,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我好崇拜你們</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們合力打造出無比美好的社群</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

41
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蛇油</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>快速舒緩）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

42
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:22,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒的粉絲描述對醫學界失望的心情</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

43
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>亦步亦趨追隨她的療癒旅程</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

44
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:26,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>吸引幾千名年輕女性</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>爭先恐後擁抱另類療法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

45
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:30,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想活下去，而且活得健康</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

46
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>各界開始提出疑問…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

47
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:47,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都不是真的嗎？她得過癌症嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

48
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:47,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的人生全毀</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

49
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-貝兒失去一切了嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-絕望…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

50
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:53,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-脆弱的粉絲怒不可遏…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-問題來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

51
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼樣的人會假裝得腦癌？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

52
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（2015年，聖摩尼加）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

53
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是根據謊言改編的真實故事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

54
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:12,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有些名字經過變更，以保護無辜的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

55
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森並沒有因為</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>她的故事搬上螢幕而得到報酬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

56
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一群混蛋</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

57
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

58
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>過濾的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

59
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:34,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，叫外賣送來的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

60
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是貝兒還是安娜貝兒？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

61
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒就可以了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

62
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我聽說你就像現實版的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>危機處理專家奧莉維亞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

63
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這樣啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

64
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的套裝更好看</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

65
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你喜歡嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

66
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:46,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拯救他人？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

67
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那些陷入危機的人？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

68
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:53,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要不要告訴我這一切是怎麼開始的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

69
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:56,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你覺得你對我了解多少？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不夠多</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

70
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:59,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-沒錯</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你是個複雜的人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

71
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>算吧，我們都是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

72
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不是特例</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

73
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>兩百萬個粉絲耶，少來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

74
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是兩百三十萬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

75
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

76
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們懂…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

77
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的粉絲知道我不會隨意批判</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

78
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人們喜歡這種態度</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

79
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以他們才會直覺地喜歡我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

80
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你收到一些死亡威脅</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

81
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“我希望她死於癌症”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

82
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很多人腦袋不清楚</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

83
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以我才來這裡…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

84
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>澄清那些誤解</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

85
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>腦袋不清楚，好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

86
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:38,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你沒有說謊或捏造事實嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

87
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有，我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

88
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不想亂貼標籤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

89
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:44,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但只有反社會人格才幹得出那種事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

90
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有反社會人格</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

91
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:50,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以馬上做50種人格測驗</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

92
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>證明我是共感人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

93
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>每次都是相同結果</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

94
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:58,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我感覺得到…各種情緒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

95
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊，那一定很心累</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

96
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有時候…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

97
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你靠拯救他人維生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

98
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我盡我所能幫助他人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

99
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>總歸一句</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

100
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我給予協助</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

101
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>各位粉絲們</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

102
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:26,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我好雀躍，等不及想跟你們分享</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

103
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當我確診罹患末期腦癌時</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

104
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:31,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知道該跟誰求助或信任誰</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

105
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:35,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我覺得孤立無援</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>意興闌珊、靈感匱乏</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

106
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:39,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>也許你沒得癌症</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但還是有類似的感受</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

107
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>知道嗎？這樣不行</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

108
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:45,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>快下載我全新的手機應用程式</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>《健康廚坊》，今天就行動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

109
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:49,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一餐一餐改變你的生活</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

110
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以，她改變了我的人生嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

111
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

112
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她有幫上忙嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

113
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我回想起認識貝兒之前的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

114
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當時這一切仍未發生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

115
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:12,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是個超級幸運兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

116
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>賈斯汀</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

117
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>露西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

118
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這種火花…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

119
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

120
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>屬於我的愛情故事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

121
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有那麼多的計畫…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

122
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>無論是荒唐還是重大的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

123
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我就是個計畫魔人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

124
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>直到某一天…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

125
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

126
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>…所有事變成一堆棘手的爛攤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

127
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

128
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>怎麼了？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

129
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你這裡有一團東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

130
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一直都在啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

131
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-這是馬文</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這樣啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

132
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-失敬失敬</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-馬文和法蘭克</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

133
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>馬文和法蘭克，打擾了，兩位</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

134
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:10,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你會忍不住想上病友論壇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

135
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拜谷歌大神找醫療資訊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

136
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>忍住衝動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

137
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有問題可以隨時寫電郵給我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

138
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會在48小時內回信</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

139
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（當你的親人罹患乳癌）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

140
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，準備進行麻醉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

141
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>深呼吸，親愛的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

142
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（化療）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

143
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>賈斯汀</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

144
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你覺得如何？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

145
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>別弄濕我！快住手</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

146
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我認得她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

147
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她會來咖啡館</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

148
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>說她有腦瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

149
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>第四期，膠質母細胞瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

150
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:02,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但她整個人煥發光采</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

151
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>活力四射</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

152
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>洋溢正能量又耀眼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

153
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:09,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她當然也做了化療</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但還找到其他療法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

154
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-兩個佛陀碗</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

155
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:13,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們家的香菇最好吃</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>是野外採的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

156
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是就好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

157
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:19,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她研發出一款不可思議的應用程式</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>造福許多人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

158
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且內容獨樹一格</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>講述她抗癌之路的真相</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

159
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>與經歷的難關</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

160
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:28,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你怎麼可能不深受啟發？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

161
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:33,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你看，她是粉絲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

162
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

163
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是你寫的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

164
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:42,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，我有在社群網站上追蹤你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

165
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你也是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

166
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乳癌，第三期</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

167
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以前也會這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

168
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>把自我認同和疾病綁在一起</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

169
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我討厭我的伴侶這樣對我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

170
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你在做…今天有什麼大計畫嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

171
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是在寫我的書</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

172
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>寫書？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

173
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-天啊，太棒了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

174
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有點激動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

175
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>內容多半是食譜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

176
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這些心得來自我的…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

177
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:17,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我本來想說"旅程"</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

178
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>其實我問過腫瘤醫生關於飲食的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

179
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她翻白眼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

180
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:24,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我必須說</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>他們對營養的知識怎麼能這麼淺薄？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

181
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真是有夠傲慢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

182
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>仔細想想，真是太沒醫德了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

183
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我等不及想看你的書</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

184
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，你應該來參加新書發表會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

185
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

186
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很樂意，那是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

187
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>多謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

188
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我愛你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

189
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一切都會沒事的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

190
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

191
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>髮色超酷的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

192
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>多謝誇獎，對，是假髮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

193
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

194
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

195
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

196
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:10,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒沒有寄邀請函來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

197
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:15,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我還是預購了她的書</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>開始照她的食譜做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

198
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我從一開始就公開說過</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

199
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:25,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是腦癌患者</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>想要尋找自然療法治癒自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

200
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>外界的迴響讓我深受感動</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

201
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>完全沒料到會這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

202
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:33,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從來沒想過</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我很驚訝我的故事能引起共鳴</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

203
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:37,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒，你覺得是什麼原因</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>讓你吸引大批粉絲？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

204
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:42,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想應該是我堅持展現真實的一面</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

205
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有太多人過度修飾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

206
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:47,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我敢說我們都有這個毛病</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

207
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以前也是這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

208
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我曾經對自己的膚況感到自卑</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

209
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小時候我的性格害羞…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

210
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>到哪裡都覺得格格不入</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

211
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但逐一檢視我擁有的東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

212
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:03,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我學會了尋找與珍惜</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>純粹與實在的事物</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

213
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:08,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>人生中最悽慘的情況之一</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

214
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就發生在我身上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

215
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你們知道嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

216
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我對此充滿感激</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

217
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好的…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

218
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>說到這個…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

219
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我還要藉這個機會</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

220
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:26,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>向我的朋友與導師致敬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

221
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

222
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很遺憾她今晚無法出席</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

223
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想你們都理解原因</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

224
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:37,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我知道這能給她帶來安慰，所以…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

225
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，收到了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

226
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>收到了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

227
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>看到有人向你致意嗎？超體貼的吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

228
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真他媽的窩心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

229
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那本書呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

230
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那些食譜…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

231
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有什麼用處嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

232
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，很不錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

233
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，小蜜</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

234
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你想要我怎麼辦？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

235
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:07,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>告訴你想要我怎麼做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

236
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會照辦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

237
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要她身敗名裂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

238
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只是假設，但我的書風評比她的好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

239
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:18,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她肯定心裡不是滋味</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

240
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:21,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不能怪她，但我的預付版稅高多了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

241
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不好意思，我不太明白</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

242
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>誰很受傷？誰的書？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

243
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定就是這個原因</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

244
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>說到底</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

245
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那就是她會做的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

246
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:37,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道《穿著Prada的惡魔》中</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>安迪大改造後</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

247
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:40,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就過得順風順水嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

248
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的感覺就是這樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

249
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蜜拉布萊克）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

250
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:52,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在大學時成績頂尖，剛剛搬到雪梨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

251
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>第一次離鄉背井</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

252
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我跟我媽一天要通三次電話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

253
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒開玩笑</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

254
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我找到我夢寐以求的新聞工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

255
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>《女朋友》雜誌，請稍等</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

256
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有一票死忠兼換帖的好友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

257
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>加上足夠的浪漫情愛調劑生活</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

258
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:11,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>雖然我本來明明可以</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

259
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:14,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>應該可以，也真的希望</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>當初能更妥善地照顧自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

260
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:17,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我才22歲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

261
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:18,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你22歲的時候在做什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

262
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:23,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，我不會念…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

263
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:26,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>未分化多型性惡性肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

264
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:31,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我幫你寫下來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

265
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

266
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:36,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>喬有基底細胞皮膚癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

267
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:39,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都怪昆士蘭的陽光</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

268
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

269
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:41,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個不一樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

270
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:45,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉手臂上的腫塊是侵襲性腫瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

271
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是一種罕見的軟組織肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

272
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:49,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，所以要怎麼辦？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

273
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:52,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要做化療還是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

274
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不要</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

275
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-寶貝…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不要</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

276
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不要，我看過外婆的慘況</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

277
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:02,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我媽因為腸癌做過化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

278
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:05,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>實際上，化療不是我的治療方案首選</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

279
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:09,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>以後當然要做</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但目前手術是我們的最佳選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

280
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:14,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你可以切除腫瘤？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

281
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:17,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，要做全身麻醉嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

282
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:23,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們可以看到肉瘤數量很多</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

283
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:25,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>表示手臂上的是轉移的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

284
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:29,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以割除個別腫瘤沒有意義</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

285
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:33,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大範圍切除更能避免</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>腫瘤擴散到手臂之外</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

286
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以還沒有擴散？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

287
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是好消息，對吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

288
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:46,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那切除範圍有多大？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

289
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:56,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（《女朋友》）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

290
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（截肢：你該知道的事）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

291
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（另類保健）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

292
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（截肢對心理的影響）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

293
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:41,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>選擇正能量</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>因為我試過沉溺於負面情緒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

294
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>結果不太好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

295
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:46,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們的內心都有個聲音</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

296
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:48,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但被外界的雜音淹沒了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

297
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:51,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果我們能停下來傾聽…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

298
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:56,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那聲音會引導我們進入崇高的境界…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

299
00:16:58,040 --> 00:17:00,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>《女朋友》雜誌</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>請問要轉哪個分機？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

300
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:06,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想大家照座位順序自我介紹</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>應該比較容易</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

301
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:08,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是修醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

302
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是卡蜜拉的腫瘤科醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

303
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:12,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>羅蘭醫生，放射科</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

304
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:14,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>西蒙史密斯瓊斯，我負責動手術</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

305
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是麥可，你的義肢製作師</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

306
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>莎莉，心理醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

307
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>艾瑪，職能治療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

308
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

309
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:25,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不認為這是正確的做法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

310
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:31,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們週三討論過</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>可能有進一步轉移的風險</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

311
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我找到一個案例研究</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

312
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:36,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有個來自曼徹斯特的女孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

313
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的脛骨有惡性骨肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

314
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她的醫療團隊建議截肢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

315
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但心理師說這可能導致</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

316
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:44,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>超出病患情緒力</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>所能承受的自我認同危機</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

317
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:48,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她選擇去柏林，進行槲寄生療法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

318
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是三年前的事了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

319
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以多印幾份給大家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

320
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:54,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你是說“槲寄生療法”嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

321
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>魯道夫史坦納</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

322
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:59,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>高劑量的槲寄生萃取物</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>可產生細胞毒素</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

323
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，沒這回事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

324
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我叫魯道夫史坦納</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

325
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:07,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的直覺來自於觀察到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

326
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:11,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>槲寄生也如同癌症，具備寄生性</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

327
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:14,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最終會殺死宿主</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

328
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:16,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>遵循赫尼曼的理論</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

329
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:18,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>亦即“以同治同”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

330
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:19,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>完全是江湖醫術</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

331
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:22,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在瑞典、荷蘭與德國</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>都已經應用在臨床上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

332
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:26,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>超過一千項體外研究顯示</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>它可促進抗癌力</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

333
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:29,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>同時也有不良反應的紀錄</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>包括嚴重過敏</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

334
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:31,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>發燒、關節痛、腎衰竭…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

335
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:33,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>當你在說我的時候，眼睛請看著我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

336
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:41,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是我的手臂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

337
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:50,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說裡面有癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

338
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>裡面有癌症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

339
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>羅蘭醫生…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

340
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有你的掃瞄片子，恐怕確實顯示</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

341
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:58,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有多處侵襲性腫瘤…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

342
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要其他選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

343
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:03,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉，我想告訴你</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>一些已經取得的進展…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

344
00:19:03,080 --> 00:19:04,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要其他選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

345
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>死亡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

346
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:07,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那是另一個選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

347
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:10,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好了，大家先冷靜一下</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你想死嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

348
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:12,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，我們再找時間討論</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

349
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:14,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這就是我們要面對的現實</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

350
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:18,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你懂不懂我試著跟你解釋的事？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

351
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:22,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你一定要明白我說的話，小姑娘</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

352
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽，對不起</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

353
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:30,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，親愛的，不用道歉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

354
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:33,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我截肢就是了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

355
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:35,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

356
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:45,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽著，如果你覺得</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我應該把它切除，我就做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

357
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:51,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但這是錯的，我知道這樣做不對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

358
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我感覺得到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

359
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

360
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:02,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不懂為什麼我們不能…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

361
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:07,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>考慮一些不同的選項</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

362
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這實在有點…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

363
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:13,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太極端了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

364
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:17,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>還有其他選擇嗎？聽你的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

365
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:20,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我強烈建議截肢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

366
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:27,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-那實驗性的…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-比如藥物試驗，拜託了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

367
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:32,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>由於來自家屬的巨大壓力</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

368
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:36,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在滿心疑慮之下</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>進行局部肢體灌注術</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

369
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這屬於實驗性手術</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>把一劑藥效強十倍的化療藥物</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

370
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:44,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>直接注射在腫瘤部位</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

371
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:50,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們發現病患對局部肢體灌注化療</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>三個月的平均反應率為58%</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

372
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:53,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但對蜜拉這類上肢疾病患者來說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

373
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>反應率下降到37%</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

374
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:57,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從另一方面來看</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

375
00:20:57,440 --> 00:21:01,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>截肢的話，她的存活率是89.9%</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

376
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:05,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我畢竟不是荳蔻年華的漂亮女孩</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>那也不是我的手臂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

377
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:14,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>難以想像他們要切除她的手臂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

378
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:18,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>幸好我們堅持到底</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

379
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:19,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

380
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>下次要聽醫生的話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

381
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:28,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們怎麼說我們就怎麼做</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

382
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

383
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:32,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不會有下次的，喬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

384
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:50,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以，你剛才提到什麼</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

385
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:54,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-父權體制，對吧？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-沒錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

386
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:56,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>造成我們彼此對立</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

387
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:59,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個市場上應該要有足夠空間</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>讓兩者並存</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

388
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-除了這個卡蜜拉…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

389
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:05,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-大家都叫她蜜拉</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-蜜拉，她被診斷出罹癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

390
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:06,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她從頭到尾都這麼說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

391
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:08,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有理由懷疑她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

392
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:10,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為以她來說，生病是真的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

393
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-海克是嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

394
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以叫你海克嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

395
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:17,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

396
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:22,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我被診斷患有第四期腦瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

397
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:23,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

398
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

399
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你確定？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

400
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>確定</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

401
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:33,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有病歷證明你罹患末期腦癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

402
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:35,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以叫人送來給你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

403
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:36,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>行，很好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

404
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你說謊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

405
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你在過程中感到迷茫</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

406
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:47,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>來這裡尋求我的專業建議與指導</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

407
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:48,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>記住這裡不會有任何批判</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

408
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:50,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

409
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:53,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那就請便吧，指導我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

410
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:56,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最好的情況，讓我把話說完…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

411
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:59,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你銷聲匿跡，改名字，找個好律師</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

412
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:02,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你應該早就要有律師了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我不能拋下我的公司，海克</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

413
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:04,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你很清楚現況</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

414
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:06,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有作品和支持者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

415
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:10,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>更別提人氣簡直…難以估量</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

416
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:11,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>都化為烏有了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

417
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:13,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-別再肖想</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好，聽著</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

418
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:17,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不是來尋求你的法律建議</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>或商業協助…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

419
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那你來這裡做什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

420
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:21,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是來找你的，特別是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

421
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:25,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我想洗刷我的名聲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

422
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:30,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>要達成目的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我需要受訪，提供我的說法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

423
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:34,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>平面宣傳、電視節目</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>或是真人實境秀都好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

424
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的身價高達七位數</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

425
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:40,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你會拿到豐厚的佣金</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

426
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:44,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你只需要打幾通電話</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

427
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:47,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我現在把一隻鞋子丟出窗外</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

428
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>隨便都能砸中十幾、二十個騙子</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

429
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:55,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我沒有說謊，好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

430
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:56,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我已經說過了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

431
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:05,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

432
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你要我幫你營造有利的氛圍嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

433
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我需要一些素材</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

434
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>坎坷的童年？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

435
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:17,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是禁忌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

436
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:19,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你受訪時已經提過</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你母親罹患多發性硬化症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

437
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不能談她</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

438
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:24,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，那心理健康呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

439
00:24:25,360 --> 00:24:28,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>多發性硬化症是身體退化</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>不是精神退化</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

440
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，我是指你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

441
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒什麼好丟臉的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

442
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:34,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道我自己有時會焦慮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

443
00:24:35,840 --> 00:24:38,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你聽說過孟求森症候群嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

444
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:43,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>指的是一個人會裝病</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>以博取同情甚至是關注</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

445
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:47,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道那是什麼，那叫孟喬森症候群</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

446
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:51,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>它不是病，而是精神疾病診斷</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>和統計手冊裡的人格障礙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

447
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:52,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你讀過了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

448
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:56,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>拜託！我不是對醫學一無所知</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

449
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:59,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我花很多時間待過很多家醫院</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

450
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:02,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我被診斷出患有惡性腦瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

451
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:04,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>被宣判剩下六星期可活</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

452
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:05,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最多四個月</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

453
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:06,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>誰說的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

454
00:25:07,040 --> 00:25:09,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-哪個醫生？哪家醫院？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我說了會把資訊給你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

455
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好，哪時？哪時候給我？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

456
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:15,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我沒辦法命令國際郵政系統</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-少來這套</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

457
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:16,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你什麼時候確診的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

458
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

459
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很努力想要幫忙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

460
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:23,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好歹能回答這個問題吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

461
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是膠質母細胞瘤嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

462
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:37,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>原來是寡樹突膠質瘤…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

463
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:39,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她住院多久了？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

464
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那段期間你肯定無法工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

465
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:44,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不該這麼做</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但我會把你的申請案列為急件</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

466
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:47,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嗯，對，我只要處理好文書就行了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

467
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:49,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>別客氣…一定要的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

468
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:51,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你的家人受了那麼多苦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

469
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:53,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>能幫上忙是我的榮幸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

470
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（2010年，墨爾本）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

471
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:59,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你們一起買的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

472
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我好喜歡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

473
00:26:02,600 --> 00:26:04,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太感動了，謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

474
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:07,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>搬到新城市真的很不容易</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

475
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:11,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但你們都這麼大方地接納我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

476
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>總之…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

477
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:19,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我非常期待接下來的冒險</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

478
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:21,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有點害怕</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

479
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:25,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我們都會盡快回來探望大家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

480
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:29,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你明天會開車來我的產前派對嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

481
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:32,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-實際上，我…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-只有我們幾個人而已</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

482
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我只想邀親近的朋友來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

483
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可以的話別發布在網路上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

484
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好，沒問題</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-太好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

485
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:40,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你會喝酒嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

486
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>會的話，你來接我，我可以開你的車</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

487
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

488
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（有機花椰菜，芹菜）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

489
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:52,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（有機青花菜，胡蘿蔔）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

490
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:24,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好，這是人家送的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>所以我沒有收據</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

491
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:27,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很喜歡，但我對合成纖維過敏</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

492
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:31,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很遺憾，沒有收據我們無法退款</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

493
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:34,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>標籤還在，看到了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

494
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你可以直接擺回架上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

495
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:39,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>換貨呢？要不要四處逛一逛？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

496
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:48,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只是…我不知道我還需不需要…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

497
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:54,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是說很有可能…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

498
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>醫生不確定她能不能撐過來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

499
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:00,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>親愛的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

500
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:04,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很遺憾，好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

501
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

502
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不希望你惹上麻煩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

503
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>反正只是蠢規定</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

504
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-25元？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-24.95元</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

505
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:23,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>促銷價</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

506
00:28:28,080 --> 00:28:29,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小氣巴拉的一群爛人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

507
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（牛奶</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>白麵包）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

508
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（雞籠蛋</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>美乃滋）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

509
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蛋糕粉）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

510
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:44,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我會去機場巴士站接你</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我在電郵裡有寫，媽</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

511
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:47,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不記得有看到電郵</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

512
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我再重寄一次</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

513
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:51,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我當然很擔心莫斯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

514
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:54,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-牠都不吃飯</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-真的嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

515
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:57,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這可不妙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

516
00:28:57,160 --> 00:29:00,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我猜可能是牠的腎臟出問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

517
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:04,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>死都不用貓砂盆</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

518
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>尿在浴室地板上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

519
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:09,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>反正我會去的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

520
00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:12,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>太好了，我有加買行李</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但不能超過15公斤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

521
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:15,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>出發去機場前，記得把行李秤重</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

522
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:17,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我非去不可，不是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

523
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:21,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我得去見一見你孩子的父親</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

524
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他會在吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

525
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:26,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不會，我跟你說過了，奈森要工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

526
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:29,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不懂他為什麼不能在墨爾本工作</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

527
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:31,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為他是飛人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

528
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你說他不是人？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

529
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是啦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

530
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:39,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-飛人，飛進飛出的人</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-原來是飛出去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

531
00:29:39,520 --> 00:29:40,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>幸好我不用</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

532
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:43,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可憐的貓咪</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

533
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:47,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>萬一我不在時，出事了怎麼辦？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

534
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我都不敢想了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

535
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:52,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們是最佳拍檔，對吧，小貓咪？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

536
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:56,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的腎痛也一直沒改善</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

537
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:59,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>派翠克醫生要我再做一次掃描</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

538
00:30:00,600 --> 00:30:02,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我得取消約診</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

539
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他會不高興的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

540
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:08,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>媽，也許你還是別來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

541
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不行，我一定要去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

542
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:15,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧，明天見10點15分</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

543
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:17,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>機場巴士站，紅色的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

544
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:23,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你不希望我去，直接說就行了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

545
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:25,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是屬於你的盛大派對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

546
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

547
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:30,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>直接告訴我你的想法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

548
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她不會來了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

549
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:50,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

550
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:53,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>快來見見妲希</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我把你的事都告訴她了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

551
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:54,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>妲希，親愛的！</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

552
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你好嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-妲希？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

553
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我很好，這地方挺不錯的</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-是啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

554
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:04,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我去弄精油</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

555
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:10,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>軟骨肉瘤，23個月前，你呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

556
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:13,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>未分化的多型性肉瘤</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

557
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>應該是最近的事吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

558
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:22,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們本來想先做保肢手術</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但後來腫瘤蔓延了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

559
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很遺憾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

560
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

561
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:29,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>艾美跟我說你做了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>試驗性的局部肢體灌注化療</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

562
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:33,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你這次要做保肢手術嗎？還是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

563
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有，實際上我正在緩解期</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

564
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那太好了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

565
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:45,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但如果你需要找人聊聊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我可以加你臉書</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

566
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:53,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好啊</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-現在仰躺著</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

567
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:57,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從肩膀開始放鬆</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

568
00:32:57,520 --> 00:33:02,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>接著放鬆你的眼睛、下巴</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

569
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:06,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>鬆開你的手指、腳趾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

570
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:09,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>用鼻子深呼吸</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

571
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:14,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>接著以大休息的狀態</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>深吸最後一口氣，徹底釋放</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

572
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我向你們致意</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-可惡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

573
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:27,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>非常感謝各位今天來上課</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

574
00:33:27,320 --> 00:33:29,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>請你們慢慢起身</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

575
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>蜜拉，嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

576
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是阿洛</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>可倫賓小學、希斯特老師的班級</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

577
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:44,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-阿洛，嗨，你好嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-嗨</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

578
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:49,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對了，我們是不是…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我們在高中畢業週激吻過吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

579
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（已刪除的檔案）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

580
00:33:54,520 --> 00:33:55,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（刪除照片）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

581
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:56,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有啦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

582
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:59,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你來這裡上什麼課？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

583
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:02,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我在…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

584
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你…對，我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

585
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我剛剛…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

586
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:08,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我很遺…對，我聽說了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

587
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:13,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-不是什麼八卦，大家都很擔心</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

588
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:15,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我聽說你狠狠反擊了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

589
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:16,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>算吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

590
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:20,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我來參加做戰勝癌症週</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>確保能把它打趴在地</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

591
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:21,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真棒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

592
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:22,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你呢？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

593
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我…來做冥想導師的訓練</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

594
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:27,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽起來很有趣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

595
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你要一起吃早餐嗎？我很想聽你分享</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

596
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:34,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我得去下一個工作坊，待會見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

597
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:36,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，沒問題</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

598
00:34:37,160 --> 00:34:38,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-謝謝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

599
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:47,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（親愛的大家，出太陽了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>快卡位！我們待會見！）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

600
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

601
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:32,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>今天天氣真好啊</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

602
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:35,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>別擔心，寶貝，我才剛到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

603
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>真糟糕</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

604
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:43,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我以前經痛也很嚴重</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

605
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:45,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這就是懷孕的好處</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

606
00:35:48,600 --> 00:35:50,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，可以試著補充一些鎂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

607
00:35:52,160 --> 00:35:54,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>如果你想來個一小時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我可以開車送你回去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

608
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，沒錯</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

609
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:01,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係，我明白</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

610
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:06,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，我還會偏頭痛呢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

611
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:10,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但聽著，我會幫你準備一個愛心包裹</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

612
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:13,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有月見草油和薑黃</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

613
00:36:14,160 --> 00:36:15,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，我會的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

614
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

615
00:36:19,640 --> 00:36:21,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，好吧，再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

616
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:07,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在連我的視線也開始模糊了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

617
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（急診室）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

618
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:11,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我媽有多發性硬化症</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

619
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:13,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這種痛感更像是…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

620
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>結構性，而不是神經性的…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

621
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好像頭裡面長東西</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

622
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:25,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個只是要固定你的頭部</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

623
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

624
00:37:57,240 --> 00:38:00,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-喂，你能不能…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-“這個消息震撼了史威特谷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

625
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:04,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>年輕漂亮的伊莉莎白韋克菲爾德</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>陷入昏迷，瀕臨死亡”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

626
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:06,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只是精神糧食而已</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

627
00:38:07,560 --> 00:38:09,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>結局是什麼？她熬過來了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

628
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個系列大概有150集</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

629
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我有東西要給你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

630
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我找到這個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

631
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:23,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>在河裡發現的，我通常不會帶走</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>但我想讓你看看這個</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

632
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:25,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>其他的…都是黑色和灰色</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

633
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但這一顆…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

634
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>與眾不同</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

635
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好美</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

636
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:39,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-留著吧</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我不需要留著</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

637
00:38:39,080 --> 00:38:40,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不，沒關係，我特地拿給你的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

638
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:45,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道嗎？我記得小學時</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你最喜歡的顏色是綠色</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

639
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:49,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你以前常在點心時間摘四葉草</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

640
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>記住這種事很奇怪</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

641
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

642
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:58,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

643
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:01,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>一定很激勵人心吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

644
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:03,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那個團體裡的能量？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

645
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:05,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

646
00:39:05,960 --> 00:39:08,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對啊，倖存者的氣場，無比強大</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

647
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:09,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是有毒才對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

648
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>病態的氣場</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

649
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:19,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你知道他們是自作自受吧？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

650
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:22,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道我是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

651
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:24,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道是我自己</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>把這些壞東西塞進身體</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

652
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:27,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-化療藥…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不是化療，我是說以前</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

653
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:31,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大學時我拚了命念書</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我以為…我不知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

654
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:35,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只要我高興</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>星期三我愛喝酒嗑藥是我的事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

655
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我很清楚</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

656
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我厭倦了當乖乖牌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

657
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:49,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我知道我咎由自取</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

658
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:55,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你戰勝病魔了，蜜拉，你做到了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不，我沒有戰勝它</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

659
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:04,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>並沒有，我下星期要切除手臂了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

660
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:16,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>現在醫生說了算</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>因為癌症復發了，而且更嚴重</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

661
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:17,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嚴重好幾倍</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

662
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:23,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我能感覺到它在我體內，我恨死它了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

663
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>而且我別無選擇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

664
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:30,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-嘿，你有很多選擇</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不，我沒有選擇了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

665
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你做什麼？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

666
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>別走，嘿</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

667
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>留下來，先別走</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

668
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:43,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

669
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

670
00:41:41,160 --> 00:41:42,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乖女孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

671
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:45,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她很勇敢，也很善良</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

672
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:47,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從不掃興，也從不發脾氣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

673
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>乖女孩</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

674
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這是我們被制約的框架</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

675
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:55,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以當醫生檢查我的身體</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>結果發現疾病時</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

676
00:41:55,640 --> 00:41:58,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不知道</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>如何用言詞來描述心中的憤怒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

677
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:04,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但這個帥氣的男子</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>當時他還不是我的男人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

678
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:07,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>送給我一塊石頭，同時提醒了我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

679
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:10,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這個世界遠比我們所稱讚的更神奇</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

680
00:42:10,200 --> 00:42:11,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>…進入獅子呼吸式</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

681
00:42:11,840 --> 00:42:15,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>吸氣時把胸部往前傾…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

682
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:20,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>聽到自己釋放的聲音…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

683
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:24,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>很好，蜜拉</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

684
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:32,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以，不再撒謊、假裝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>也不再取悅他人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

685
00:42:33,440 --> 00:42:36,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從現在起，我要停止用腦袋思考</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

686
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:38,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>開始用身體去感受</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

687
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:42,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>因為我知道切除手臂是錯的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

688
00:42:43,720 --> 00:42:46,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>就好像我知道化療很不妥</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

689
00:42:48,640 --> 00:42:50,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我必須找到正確的方法</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

690
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為了我自己</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

691
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>早安，這裡是峇里島烏布鎮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

692
00:42:59,480 --> 00:43:03,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊，這幾天真是棒呆了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

693
00:43:03,320 --> 00:43:06,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>跟很多人來自世界各地的勵志女性</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

694
00:43:06,720 --> 00:43:09,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>交流與分享經驗</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

695
00:43:09,120 --> 00:43:11,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-小露？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-如果你覺得自己精疲力盡</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

696
00:43:11,080 --> 00:43:13,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>或被折磨得不成人形</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我完全能體會…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

697
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:16,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你能試著睡覺嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-…像這些不可思議的地方…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

698
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:20,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我把聲音關小一點</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-…比如墨西哥的赫希研究所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

699
00:43:21,240 --> 00:43:23,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>他們治療整個人</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

700
00:43:23,280 --> 00:43:26,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>從毒性的源頭下手</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>而不是治標不治本</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

701
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:29,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，所以我…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

702
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:32,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>週四跟你見面</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

703
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:36,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，很快打擾一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

704
00:43:37,680 --> 00:43:39,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想請問關於…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

705
00:43:39,800 --> 00:43:42,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有朋友推薦一家墨西哥的治療中心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

706
00:43:42,880 --> 00:43:43,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>誰？哪位朋友？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

707
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:45,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>叫做赫希研究所</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

708
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:47,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒吉柏森？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

709
00:43:47,680 --> 00:43:49,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-她的朋友</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你是3C期</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

710
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:52,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>進入3C期我們不能亂來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

711
00:43:52,760 --> 00:43:55,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒有3D期，下個階段就是末期了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

712
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:57,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你很清楚末期會怎樣</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

713
00:43:58,560 --> 00:43:59,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

714
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:00,800
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

715
00:44:08,080 --> 00:44:09,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝謝你撥冗，醫生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

716
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:12,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>星期四她一定要回診</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

717
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:15,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她真他媽的傲慢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

718
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:17,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我想聽，我想聽到她親口說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

719
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:20,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她為什麼不能直接承認治療無效？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

720
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:22,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我不知道</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-這種一體適用的治療思維</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

721
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:24,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-太離譜了</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我們沒有資格做…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

722
00:44:25,560 --> 00:44:27,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-怎麼了？你喘不過氣嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我沒事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

723
00:44:28,440 --> 00:44:29,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不是我的照顧者</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

724
00:44:33,160 --> 00:44:35,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你本來應該是…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-過來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

725
00:44:35,080 --> 00:44:36,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好了，聽我說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

726
00:44:38,320 --> 00:44:39,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>這一點都不性感</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

727
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:42,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我不覺得</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

728
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:44,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好噁心</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

729
00:44:46,560 --> 00:44:49,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我令人噁心，我不想一直有這種感覺</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

730
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:51,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

731
00:44:52,400 --> 00:44:54,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那你有什麼替代選項，小露？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

732
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:55,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那家墨西哥醫院嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

733
00:44:55,680 --> 00:44:58,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我絕不允許一個穿了破鼻環的網紅</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

734
00:44:58,480 --> 00:45:00,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>破壞多年的實際醫學研究結果</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

735
00:45:00,680 --> 00:45:03,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你不允許？好極了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

736
00:45:06,440 --> 00:45:07,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我自己可以起來</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

737
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:14,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對不起</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

738
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:16,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>沒關係</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

739
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對不起</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

740
00:45:20,560 --> 00:45:22,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們沒事，謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

741
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:30,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你還好嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

742
00:45:30,720 --> 00:45:32,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不用了，謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

743
00:45:54,080 --> 00:45:56,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>身為生第一胎的準媽媽</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我本來很希望</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

744
00:45:56,760 --> 00:46:00,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>那些自稱是我朋友的人</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>給我多一點關心與支持</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

745
00:46:00,800 --> 00:46:02,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我知道大家的生活都很忙</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

746
00:46:02,920 --> 00:46:06,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我盡量不抱怨，但我接二連三碰上</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

747
00:46:06,200 --> 00:46:08,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可怕的病症，現在心情很煎熬</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

748
00:46:08,520 --> 00:46:12,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>可惡，我本來非常期待</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>辦我的產前派對</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

749
00:46:14,320 --> 00:46:15,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>親愛的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

750
00:46:15,560 --> 00:46:16,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>給你抱抱</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

751
00:46:16,800 --> 00:46:18,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>什麼可怕的病症？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

752
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:28,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（親愛的，給你抱抱</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>什麼可怕的病症？）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

753
00:46:33,440 --> 00:46:36,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我好像提過我長期飽受偏頭痛所苦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

754
00:46:37,080 --> 00:46:38,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我沒有透露一件事</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

755
00:46:38,600 --> 00:46:41,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我最近在上班時發作，然後暈倒了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

756
00:46:42,200 --> 00:46:44,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我剛從醫院回到家</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

757
00:46:44,480 --> 00:46:45,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我的醫生說…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

758
00:46:47,840 --> 00:46:49,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“你得了腦癌”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

759
00:46:52,160 --> 00:46:55,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（刪除）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

760
00:46:56,600 --> 00:46:57,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

761
00:47:00,080 --> 00:47:03,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>“你得了惡性腦癌</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

762
00:47:03,720 --> 00:47:04,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你快死了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

763
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:06,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>只剩下六星期的壽命</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

764
00:47:07,480 --> 00:47:09,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>最多四個月”</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

765
00:47:10,160 --> 00:47:12,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>但我要證明他錯了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

766
00:47:12,320 --> 00:47:15,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>為了我自己和我的寶寶</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

767
00:47:15,880 --> 00:47:17,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我一定要活下去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

768
00:47:20,680 --> 00:47:23,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>天啊，親愛的，這太不公平了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

769
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:26,280
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-可憐的寶貝</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-很難過聽到這件事，親愛的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

770
00:47:26,360 --> 00:47:28,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-可憐的小傢伙…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你真勇敢</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

771
00:47:28,280 --> 00:47:29,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>有需要幫忙盡管說</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

772
00:47:29,560 --> 00:47:32,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-好可怕</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-有什麼需要就告訴我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

773
00:47:32,160 --> 00:47:34,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-需要協助請跟我說</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我看到都哭了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

774
00:47:34,240 --> 00:47:36,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我甚至無法想像…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

775
00:47:38,320 --> 00:47:40,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>說真的，我們都在這裡支持你</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

776
00:47:40,840 --> 00:47:42,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你很堅強</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你一定會撐過去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

777
00:47:44,280 --> 00:47:45,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你可能會喜歡這個部落格</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

778
00:47:45,840 --> 00:47:47,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>她跟你很像</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

779
00:47:47,240 --> 00:47:49,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（蜜拉布萊克</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>綠石療癒）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

780
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:53,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>（關於蜜拉布萊克）</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

781
00:47:54,920 --> 00:47:58,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>每天在這趟…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我真的很討厭"旅程"這個詞</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

782
00:47:58,520 --> 00:48:02,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我覺得我的聲音</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>遠比過去更堅定、響亮</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

783
00:48:03,480 --> 00:48:05,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我並不孤單，也沒有崩潰</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

784
00:48:06,560 --> 00:48:09,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我可以招搖，可以彰顯存在感</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

785
00:48:10,840 --> 00:48:12,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我比我知道的更堅強</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

786
00:48:12,960 --> 00:48:16,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以看看外面的世界，聽我咆哮吧</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

787
00:48:19,520 --> 00:48:20,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>嘿，小蜜…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

788
00:48:21,880 --> 00:48:23,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你想要我怎麼辦？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

789
00:48:23,600 --> 00:48:25,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>告訴你想要我怎麼做，我會照辦</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

790
00:48:30,640 --> 00:48:31,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我要她身敗名裂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

791
00:48:38,480 --> 00:48:41,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>改變你的身材，找到你的靈魂</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

792
00:48:42,640 --> 00:48:44,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>靠，我好愛厲害的行銷話術</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

793
00:48:44,680 --> 00:48:45,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我們還沒見過面</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

794
00:48:45,720 --> 00:48:48,000
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我是貝兒的前經紀人</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>蜜拉交情最久的朋友</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

795
00:48:48,080 --> 00:48:49,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>幾乎是這個故事的英雄</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

796
00:48:49,480 --> 00:48:51,320
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>先自我介紹一下</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

797
00:48:51,400 --> 00:48:55,560
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我16歲高中畢業</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>未滿20歲就當上投銀分析師</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

798
00:48:55,640 --> 00:48:58,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>非常消耗心神，四個月後就辭職了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

799
00:48:58,800 --> 00:49:02,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>之後搬到柏林</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>成立擁有社交影響力的孵化器</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

800
00:49:02,240 --> 00:49:05,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>工作內容變得太有趣</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>我的嬌小身軀無法負荷</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

801
00:49:05,560 --> 00:49:07,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以我決定打道回府</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

802
00:49:07,320 --> 00:49:10,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>今天有人要親自跟我見面</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

803
00:49:10,920 --> 00:49:12,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好極了</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

804
00:49:12,160 --> 00:49:14,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，這樣很好，我30分鐘後就能到</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

805
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:15,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

806
00:49:18,080 --> 00:49:20,120
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你是調查組的？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

807
00:49:20,200 --> 00:49:21,760
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，唯一還活躍的組別</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

808
00:49:21,840 --> 00:49:23,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你好，麻煩給我豆奶馥列白</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

809
00:49:23,600 --> 00:49:25,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你真的不要…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-對，我有水，謝謝</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

810
00:49:26,040 --> 00:49:27,400
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>謝了，再見</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

811
00:49:27,480 --> 00:49:29,040
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>尚恩，你吃全素嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

812
00:49:29,120 --> 00:49:30,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>不是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

813
00:49:30,160 --> 00:49:33,240
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>所以你只是…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>你點豆奶只是喜歡味道嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

814
00:49:33,320 --> 00:49:34,920
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>想吃得更健康而已</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

815
00:49:35,800 --> 00:49:36,840
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>並不是</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

816
00:49:37,600 --> 00:49:39,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>未必更健康，因為…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

817
00:49:39,520 --> 00:49:43,520
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>大豆的異黃酮是類雌激素</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>會刺激細胞增生</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

818
00:49:43,600 --> 00:49:46,440
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你應該做點功課</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-好，我會的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

819
00:49:46,520 --> 00:49:47,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-所以你叫香奈爾？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

820
00:49:47,800 --> 00:49:49,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>對，出爾反爾的爾</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

821
00:49:49,680 --> 00:49:51,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>你有梅爾吉勃遜的資訊要給我</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

822
00:49:53,000 --> 00:49:57,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我同事轉告我你急著要爆料</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>是關於…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

823
00:49:57,720 --> 00:49:58,880
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>貝兒</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

824
00:50:00,320 --> 00:50:01,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>是貝兒吉柏森</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

825
00:50:01,840 --> 00:50:02,960
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>好，那是誰？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

826
00:50:03,560 --> 00:50:06,160
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>問得好，你有多少時間…</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

827
00:50:06,240 --> 00:50:08,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>小賈！你要去聽證會了嗎？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

828
00:50:08,680 --> 00:50:11,680
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-對，我有犯罪案件</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-我不介意跟著一起去</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

829
00:50:11,760 --> 00:50:12,640
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>先生？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

830
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:17,600
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>抱歉，香奈爾</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>這位是賈斯汀，也是調查組的</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

831
00:50:18,240 --> 00:50:20,480
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-你聽說過貝兒吉柏森嗎？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-不是梅爾吉勃遜喔</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

832
00:50:22,240 --> 00:50:24,200
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-貝兒，為什麼問她？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你知道她？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

833
00:50:25,360 --> 00:50:28,360
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-露西有追蹤她，為什麼問？</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你覺得她怎麼樣？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

834
00:50:31,160 --> 00:50:33,720
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>-我沒見過她</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-你的直覺怎麼說？</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

835
00:50:36,360 --> 00:50:38,080
<c.traditionalchinese><c.bg_transparent>我覺得也許是榨財的吸血蟲</c.bg_transparent></c.traditionalchinese>

836
00:50:39,160 --> 00:50:40,920
